We denote

   $\boldsymbol {A}(\boldsymbol {J}_{i},\boldsymbol {J}_{j})^{-1}=\boldsymbol {\Sigma }^{-1}+\boldsymbol {J}_{i}\boldsymbol {J}_{i}^{T}+\boldsymbol {J}_{j}\boldsymbol {J}_{j}^{T} $

and

